sourcesContent: import React from 'react' const CasesByCountry = ({countries}) => { return ( <> # Country Active Cases Today Cases Case/Test Dead/Pop. Dead/Recv. {countries.map((countryData, key) => ( {key} {countryData.country} {countryData.cases} {countryData.cases} {countryData.todayCases} {countryData.cases} {countryData.cases} ))} ) } export default CasesByCountry;
